{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_03_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 楽しく踊ってる方がいい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、どうしよっかなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ what should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ what’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hi‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんとの期間限定ユニットが決まってから\nず～っと考えてるんだよね、怜ちゃんのこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I was teamed up with Rei-chan temporarily‚\nI can’t stop thinking about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんとの関係が気になっちゃって\nなんだかな～って感じ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m worried about her relationship with her dad.\nWondering how that’s all going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜のお父さんは……\n芸能活動のことをよく思ってないみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei’s dad?\nHe doesn't seem to like her being in the biz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのダンスは抜群にかっこいいけど\n最近はなんか鬼気迫るっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan’s dancing is outstandingly cool‚\nbut she’s a bit crazed recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.60000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "昔のグランプリの頃のリズノワみたいなんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like LizNoir was during the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……最近の怜はどこか危うさを感じるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Rei has felt a bit on-edge recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はお父さんとお母さんが応援してくれるから\nなんにも心配しないで気持ちよく踊れるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My own mom and dad are behind me all the way.\nThat’s why I’m also so carefree when I dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんも、ビシバシー！　って感じじゃなくて\nいつもみたいに楽しく踊ってる方がいいと思うんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan feels so business-like‚ so precise.\nI wish she’d have more fun while she dances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は、怜の活動がお父さんに\n認められてほしいと思ってるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ do you want Rei’s father\nto accept what she’s chosen to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "……うん。怜ちゃん、最近練習中に\nあんまり笑ってくれなくて、寂しいんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. During practice recently‚\nRei-chan doesn’t smile at all. It makes me sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺も手伝おうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you want me to help out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとに！？\n……あー、でもなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You will?!\n…Hmmm‚ hold on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7443900426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "今回は怜ちゃんと芽衣のユニットなんだし\n芽衣が頑張ってみるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei is the one who has been paired up with her.\nMei’ll try and make this work myself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "う～……{user}さ～ん……\n芽衣はもうダメかもしれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm… {user}-san!\nI’m not sure I’m cut out for this after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ、芽衣？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened‚ Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんがお父さんに認めてもらうなら\nまずは二人で話さなきゃーって思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Rei-chan’s dad is going to accept her‚\nthey need to sit down and talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、どうやってそこまで持っていったらいいか\n分かんなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don’t know how to get things to that point.\nNo idea at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "『お父さんとお母さんがどれだけ大事な存在か』って\n怜ちゃんに沢山話したら、困った顔されちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I talked to Rei-chan about how important parents are\nand she just looked kinda confused and annoyed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃまあ……いきなり熱弁されたら驚くだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is a bit of a strange topic to just launch into.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、ほんとどうしたらいいんだろう……？\n頭がパンクしそうだよ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ so what should I do instead?\nI can’t get my head around this one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時は気分転換をした方がいいぞ\n少し散歩でもしないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like you need a change of pace.\nShall we take a walk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "は～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes~~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.0000000000173,
          "startTime": 150.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 150.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 150.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふ～ん♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "La la lah~~♪",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "切り替えが早いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure switch pace fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 157.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、そうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe. You think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 160.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、このアクセ\n怜ちゃんに似合いそうだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that accessory!\nIt would look great on Rei-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4666666667,
